---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — Tony Ciencia" description="Tony Ciencia LLC Privacy Policy — how we collect, use and protect your personal information.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-inner">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

      <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
      <p>Tony Ciencia LLC, registered in New Mexico, USA (8206 Louisiana Blvd NE, Ste A #6812, Albuquerque, NM 87113). Contact: <a href="mailto:contact@tonyciencia.com">contact@tonyciencia.com</a></p>

      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly (name, email when subscribing or contacting us) and technical data collected automatically (IP address, browser type, pages visited, session duration) through cookies and analytics tools.</p>

      <h2>3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
      <p>We use your data to: send the newsletter if you have subscribed; respond to inquiries; improve site performance and content; comply with legal obligations.</p>

      <h2>4. Legal Basis</h2>
      <p>Processing is based on your consent (subscription, contact form) or the legitimate interest of Tony Ciencia LLC (site usage analytics).</p>

      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your data while your subscription is active or until you request deletion. Analytics data is retained in aggregate, anonymized form.</p>

      <h2>6. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your data. We may share it with essential service providers (hosting, email marketing) who act as data processors under confidentiality agreements.</p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict or object to the processing of your data, and to data portability. Exercise these rights by writing to <a href="mailto:contact@tonyciencia.com">contact@tonyciencia.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>
      <p>We apply appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information against unauthorized access, loss or destruction.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy at any time. The date of last review appears at the bottom of this page.</p>

      <p class="legal-reviewed">Last reviewed: May 6, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: var(--spacing-16) var(--spacing-6); }
  .legal-inner { max-width: var(--content-width); margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-inner h1 { font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); }
  .legal-inner h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: 600; margin-top: var(--spacing-10); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-reviewed { margin-top: var(--spacing-12); font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--color-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-top: var(--spacing-4); }
</style>
